item.title: DFW-12-series-cable-distribution-box
item.description: DFW-12 outdoor high-voltage cable distribution box is specially used at the cable node of AC 12kV cable system to distribute electric energy. Its connection method is simple and convenient, and has the characteristics of full insulation, full sealing, corrosion resistance, maintenance-free, and exposed safety parts. It solves the problems of cable T connection and ring network power supply with multiple incoming and outgoing lines with advanced technology.

item.title: DFW-12-outdoor-opening-and-closing-station-cable-distribution-box
item.description: DFW series European-style high-voltage cable branch box is widely used in the node connection of 10KV cable system, and is the main electrical equipment for collecting and branching cables after they come out of the switch cabinet. DFW branch box is designed for outdoor maintenance-free operation, safe and reliable, its protection level is IP33~IP66, and the underground tap can withstand flooding.

item.title: DFW-40.5-outdoor-opening-and-closing-station
item.description: ZGS-12 intelligent integrated substation American box substation is also called prefabricated substation or prefabricated substation. It is a kind of high-voltage switchgear, distribution transformer and low-voltage power distribution device. It is a factory prefabricated indoor and outdoor compact power distribution equipment arranged according to a certain wiring scheme, which is to organically combine functions such as transformer step-down and low-voltage power distribution.
